<div type="addressee"><ab facs="#facs_605_r1l1"><expan>Leẅpold<ex>en</ex></expan> von vvolframſtorff </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_605_r1l2"><expan>geſeſſ<ex>en</ex></expan> ʒu der Ruthe </ab>
</div>
